snippet.title: OMNN Teaser (Wishlist Now)
snippet.description:
NSY 10,006, It is the waning days of the emperor Neath Ithicia’m the second. No clear heir to the throne of the Galactic Ithicia’m Empire exists. Follow the secretive Black Matter Adventists as they hatch a plot to take power over the throne.

OMNN is a grand space opera inspired by various Sci-Fi media and vintage 3D games. Experience a grand plot to undermine universal power.

Published in collaboration with Dark Union: https://dark-union.org/

Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3585620/OMNN/
